Name: Super Arcade Boy in Defender of Planet Earth
About the game: A Retro Style Classic Side-Scrolling Shoot'em Up! Super Arcade Boy's Debut! Meet Super Arcade Boy, an arcade champion in the past, and now a planetary freedom fighter. Fly him through 8 levels while defeating waves of enemies and bosses. Have amusing conversations with the aliens you are destined to defeat. Then ultimately save planet Earth from being attacked! FEATURES - 8 Levels with Bosses. - Power-ups. - Amusing Dialogue between Aliens and Super Arcade Boy. - Retro Style Classic. - Waves of Enemies. - HD Graphics. - Gamepad Support. Super Arcade Boy's up to the challenge. ARE YOU?
